<div id="descriptionContainer">
  
      <div id="description" class="readable stacked" style="right:0">
        
<span id="freeTextContainer433202772617673133"><p>M. R. James is widely regarded as the father of the modern ghost story, and his tales have influenced horror writers from H. P. Lovecraft to Stephen King. First published in the early 1900s, they have never been out of print, and are recognized as classics of the genre. This collection contains some of his most chilling tales, including <i>A View from a Hill, Rats, A School S</i></p></span>
  <span id="freeText433202772617673133" style="display:none"><p>M. R. James is widely regarded as the father of the modern ghost story, and his tales have influenced horror writers from H. P. Lovecraft to Stephen King. First published in the early 1900s, they have never been out of print, and are recognized as classics of the genre. This collection contains some of his most chilling tales, including <i>A View from a Hill, Rats, A School Story, The Ash Tree,</i> and <i>The Story of a Disappearance and an Appearance</i>. Read by BAFTA and Emmy-award winning actor Derek Jacobi, and with haunting and evocative music, these tales cannot fail to send a shiver down your spine.</p><p></p></span>
  <a data-text-id="433202772617673133" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

